# Quick-start index — environment files have been split per service.
#
# Before running `make up-build`, copy each example to its live counterpart:
#
#   copy config\postgres.env.example config\postgres.env
#   copy config\backend.env.example  config\backend.env
#   copy config\frontend.env.example config\frontend.env
#
# Each file is documented with variable descriptions and safe defaults.
# See docs/DOCKER.md for a full variable reference.
#
# The .env files are git-ignored; never commit secrets.
